
[1]avoirdupois

   AVOIRDUPOIS', n. s as z. [See Poise.]

   A weight, of which a pound contains 16 ounces. Its proportion to a
   pound Troy is as 17 to 14. this is the weight for the larger and
   coarser commodities, as hay, iron, cheese, groceries, &c.
